  <name>WallyHaze</name>
  <summary>Beautiful wallpaper browser and setter with infinite scroll</summary>
  <description>
    <p>
      WallyHaze is a modern, cross-platform wallpaper browser that connects to Wallhaven.cc
      to provide an endless stream of high-quality wallpapers. With smooth infinite scrolling,
      perfect image scaling, and one-click wallpaper setting for both desktop and lock screen,
      WallyHaze makes finding and applying beautiful wallpapers effortless.
    </p>
    <p>Features:</p>
    <ul>
      <li>Infinite scroll wallpaper browser with automatic page loading</li>
      <li>Latest wallpapers sorted by date added by default</li>
      <li>Perfect image scaling without stretching or distortion</li>
      <li>One-click setup for both desktop and lock screen wallpapers</li>
      <li>Advanced search and filtering options (category, purity, sorting)</li>
      <li>High-quality wallpaper downloads in full resolution</li>
      <li>Keyboard shortcuts for efficient navigation</li>
      <li>Beautiful dark theme interface</li>
      <li>Cross-platform support (Linux and Windows)</li>
    </ul>
    <p>
      Browse thousands of beautiful wallpapers from Wallhaven.cc with a smooth,
      Instagram-like infinite scroll experience. Simply scroll down to automatically
      load more wallpapers, click any image to preview it in full resolution,
      and set it as your desktop or lock screen wallpaper with a single click.
    </p>
  </description>
